right, and Japanese business leaders were honored at chamber's Inaugural Ball 
at Century Plaza. From left, Takao Kawamura, Sheldon Ausman, Susumu Ozawa, 
Argue, Yoshimichi Ohara. ELLEN JASKOL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
