<P>
Director Alan Parker, who has two Golden Globe award nominations for 
"Mississippi Burning," has signed a three-year production and development 
agreement with Tri-Star Pictures. Tri-Star will have exclusive, first-look 
rights to film projects that Parker develops. The deal also enables Parker to 
