<DOCNO> LA011989-0057 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 7161 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 19, 1989, Thursday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 16; Column 5 
</P>
