<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The three players who led Paraguay to a Davis Cup victory over the United 
States in 1987 were named to the team that will face the Americans Feb. 3-5 at 
Ft. Myers, Fla., in a first-round World Group match. 
</P>
<P>
Selected were Victor Pecci, Hugo Chapacu and Francisco Gonzales, along with 
newcomer Rubin Alvarenga. 
</P>
